                    <li>Create a Discord account if you don't have one (it's free!)...</li>
                    <li> ...or click "Already have an account link? Log in" at the bottom of the modal</li>
                    <li>Once you're in the server, introduce yourself in the <strong>#introductions</strong> channel</li>
                    <li>And browse other channels to find topics that interest you</li>
                </ul>
